      <div class="view-content">
          <div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-title"><h1 class="field-content">The Digital Regulation Handbook: A guide for digital transformation </h1></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-authors"><span class="field-content"><ul><li><a href="/team/roku-fukui" hreflang="en">Roku Fukui</a></li></ul></span></span>|<span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content"><time datetime="2021-07-15T12:00:00Z">July 15, 2021</time>
